liuliu_exam

行业的热度

按行业对企业分组，由高至低看看各个行业的占比

raw %>% 
    count(industry) %>% 
    ggplot(aes(x = reorder(industry, -n), y = n)) + 
    geom_point(shape = 7) +
    geom_line(group = 1) +
    labs(x=" ", y = " ")

除了数量以外，让我们看看各个行业内的企业估值。在具体操作之前，我们先探索估值的分布以排除任何可能出现的离群点

raw %>% 
    count(valuation) %>% 
    ggplot(aes(x = valuation, y = n)) + 
    geom_bar(stat = "identity", width = 2, col = "salmon") +
    labs(x = "valuation", y = "count")

可以看出，前 3 名企业的估值大大压缩了估值的分布，针对以下图表我们选择把他们移除在外

raw_new <- raw %>% filter(ranking > 3) 
    raw_new %>% 
    ggplot(aes(x = industry, y = valuation)) +
    geom_point(aes(size = valuation, color = valuation), alpha = 0.8) +
    labs(title = "胡润大中华区独角兽", subtitle = "企业估值", x = "", y = "") +
    theme(legend.position="none") 

raw %>% 
    count(headquarter) %>% 
    mutate(prop = n/sum(n)) %>% 
    ggplot(aes(x = reorder(headquarter, n), y = prop * 100)) +
               geom_bar(stat = "identity", width = .2, fill = "lightblue") + 
               geom_point(size = 3, col = "navyblue") +
               coord_flip() +
    geom_text (aes(label = paste(round(prop*100, 1), "%", sep='')), nudge_y = 3)+
    labs(x = " ", y = "占比%")

地域的差异

location <- c("北京", "上海")
raw %>% 
    filter(headquarter %in% location) %>% 
    ggplot(aes(x = industry, name_zh )) +
    geom_point(aes(color = headquarter, size = valuation), position = "jitter") +
    scale_color_brewer(palette = "Set2") +
    facet_wrap(~headquarter, ncol = 1) +
    labs(x = " ", y = " ") +
    theme(axis.text.y = element_blank(), axis.ticks.y = element_blank())
